  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Glutamate is known to be a mediator for apoptosis after brain hypoxia e.g. due to cardiac
      arrest. This pilot trial evaluates the possibility of elimination of Glutamate by CRRT after
      cardiac arrest.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
